%h2
  Pipeline of Campaign
  = succeed ':' do
    = "##{campaign.id}"
  &= campaign.title

%p
  There are
  = campaign.pipeline_count
  recipient(s) in the pipeline:

- campaign.pipeline.each do |r|
  %p
    %a{ href: iri.cut('/recipient').add(id: r['rid']) }= r['email']
    with letter
    %a{ href: iri.cut('/letter').add(id: r['lid']) }= "##{r['lid']}"
